{"tid":2225842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［101 國殤] 十.一 截至晚上10時，多區共有至少86人被捕","createTime":"2020-10-01T15:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:33:55.000Z","uid":133042,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b5f2ea632be81bcdcab7348941838144848fef0","tid":2225842,"uid":133042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3SrL4o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3SrL4o.jpg&h=0a7515ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方稱截至晚上10時，多區共有至少86人被捕。其中74人包括4名區議員涉嫌於銅鑼灣區參與未經批准的集結；其餘被捕人分別涉嫌觸犯管有攻擊性武器，未能出示有效身份證明文件，管有偽造身份證，在公眾地方行為不檢和駕駛無牌車輛等罪行。此外，警方今日共票控20人涉嫌參與受禁羣組聚集，違反《預防及控制疾病(禁止羣組聚集)規例》。<br />\n<br />\n#公眾安全情報"},{"pid":"b54c1f30febbef0973df7b016d86211059ad6714","tid":2225842,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:26:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f73f2cad6af7346342b685fa0ae952522fa286f","tid":2225842,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6Qdq4V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6Qdq4V.png&h=c1cf5226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藏有攻擊性武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f20fb903d74b26eb2c1723218dda03e7dece25","tid":2225842,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f73f2cad6af7346342b685fa0ae952522fa286f","tid":2225842,"uid":16676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c6Qdq4V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc6Qdq4V.png&h=c1cf5226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藏有攻擊性武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"<